<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    {{> header}}
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./styles/chat.css" type="text/css" />
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">

        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-light">
            {{> navbar }}
        </nav>

 
        <div class="container row">
           <h2>Hola {{userLoggedIn}}</h2>
           <h3>Sala de chat</h3>
        </div>

    </div>
    
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h4>Server status</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <span class="server-online text-success">ONLINE</span>
                <span class="server-offline text-danger">OFFLINE</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            
            <div class="col-md-6">
                
                <div>

                    <form>
                        <label for="nombre" class="form-label">De:</label>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <input class="form-control" type="text" placeholder="{{userEmailLoggedIn}}" aria-label="Disabled input example" disabled>
                            <input type="hidden" id="mail" value="{{userEmailLoggedIn}}">
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                          <label for="nombre" class="form-label">Asunto</label>
                          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="subject" name="subject">
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3 form-floating">
                            <textarea class="form-control" placeholder="Leave a comment here" id="comments" name="comments"></textarea>
                            <label for="comments">Comentarios</label>
                          </div>
                        <button type="button" id="send-msg" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
                      </form>

                </div>

            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6">
                
                <div class="msgs-title">
                    <h5>Mensajes</h5>
                </div>

                <div class="msgs-container">

                    <div class="mb-3 item-chat">
                        <div class="item-header"><p><span class="msg-mail">testing@gmail.com</span> <span class="msg-date float-end">[ 2022-08-29 20:27:00 ]</span></p></div>
                        <div class="item-body"><p>Este es el cuerpoo del mensaje de los integrantes del chat</p></div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-3 item-chat">
                        <div class="item-header"><p><span class="msg-mail">mai@gmail.com</span> <span class="msg-date float-end">[ 2022-08-29 20:27:00 ]</span></p></div>
                        <div class="item-body"><p>Hola gente como estan! Todo bien por aca??</p></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        
        </div>
    </div>


    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0-beta1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="./socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
    <script src="./js/chat.js"></script>
</body>
</html>